1 SECTION 2. Chapter 342D, Hawaii Revised Statutes, is
2 amended by adding a new section to be appropriately designated
3 and to read as follows:
4 "§342D- Individual wastewater system; dwelling units.
5 An individual wastewater system may serve up to five bedrooms,
6 regardless of the number of:
7 (1) Dwellings or dwelling units; or
8 (2) Accessory units as defined by the counties,
9 whether the dwellings, dwelling units, or accessory units are
10 attached or detached; provided that this section shall not apply
11 to any new requests to connect additional dwelling units to an
12 existing cesspool."
13 SECTION 3. New statutory material is underscored.
14 SECTION 4. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.
